            . I am the wife of William Arden. I lost this handkerchief out of my room on the 23d of May; I had put it into a basket for a gentleman whom I wash for, about ten minutes before the prisoner came in - I have known him about two months.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280529-162-person931">
                  THOMAS 
                  MATTHEWS
               <interp inst="t18280529-162-person931" type="surname" value="MATTHEWS"></interp>
